+ @@ @@
+ What on Earth am I looking at?
Fuck if I know.
+ No seriously what on //Earth// am I looking at?
Are you sick and tired of your perfectly readable page being intruded upon by pesky little things like "color" and "imagination" and "readability"? Perhaps you really like the color scheme of white, more white, even more white, yet more white, did I mention whiâ€” oh yeah also blue. Or perhaps you're a masochistic?

In any case, Wikifot Theme is the theme for you!
+ @@ @@
+ Usage
To use Wikifot Theme, on any wiki, copy this string to any part of your page:
[[code]][[include :scp-wiki:theme:wikifot]][[/code]]

It should be noted that removing the ":scp-wiki:" will cause the theme to break when used on other wikis. As such it is recommend you save yourself the eyesore and yuck it to the abyssal pit from whence it came.
[[code]][[include theme:wikifot]][[/code]]
