+ Custom DIVs
Wikifot Theme provides a variety of colorful, flashy, seizure inducing DIV boxes for you to plaster all over your page with reckless abandon! Here's a few examples:
> {{@@[[div class="blockquote"]]@@}}
> Classic 'Ol Blockquote!
> {{[[/div]]}}
